author: Kam Dhillon
title: Feast Your Eyes on More Killer Street Style from Tokyo
text:
Visit the original post to see all 27 images from this gallery. 
Location: Tokyo, Japan
Season: FW17
Key Looks: A lesson in color coordination (slide #10), furry Supreme on show (#slide 10), Mademoiselle Yulia offers a murderous lesson in clashing with clarity (slide #13), sensory overload at its finest (slide #17), and that squared-out silhouette is standout (slide #27).
Editor’s Notes: Following our last street style round-up , the Japanese continue to prove they’re the masters of spring-time steez with an array of killer looks. The main trend takeaway? Defy the tunnel vision of trend-led movements and clash away.
For more Tokyo street style, check out the 25 best sneakers spotted at Tokyo Fashion Week FW17 .
